Figures

Interface FigureOperable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Circle, Drawing, Figure, Rectangle

    public interface FigureOperable
    An interface that implement all Figure, and allows to accept visitors in order to use the Visitor pattern.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Figure accept(FigureVisitor figureVisitor)
      Tha accept method allows visitors to make changes (which actually are new Figures as result).
